(3831, 2, '2015-08-14 17:35:19', '2015-08-14 10:35:19', '<strong>Juventus mun c 2 tin v Chelsea; Otamendi ang rt gn M.U; nh v ch Copa America 2015 n Leverkusen... l nhng tin chuyn nhng ng ch  24h qua.</strong>\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/13/8/cuadradoramiresjuve.jpg" alt="Chelsea s bn Cuadrado v Ramires cho Juve?" />Chelsea s bn Cuadrado v Ramires cho Juve?</div>\r\n- Juventus va ln k hoch hi mua b i tin v Juan Cuadrado v Ramires ca Chelsea sau khi h  chia tay Andrea Pirlo (sang New York City), Arturo Vidal (Juventus) cn mc tiu Julian Draxler (Schalke) nm ngoi tm vi.\r\n\r\n- Everton  k hp ng vi hu v 18 tui <span id="result_box" class="" lang="vi"><span class="hps">Holgate</span> <span class="hps">Mason (Barnley) vi gi 2 triu bng. Mason c mua v  d phng trng hp John Stones sang Chelsea. </span></span>\r\n\r\n- <a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/59/128530/ra-gia-29-trieu-euro-arsenal-quyet-vuot-mat-juve-o-vu-draxler.bdplus">Arsenal  gi n Schalke mc gi 29 triu euro cho tin v Julian Draxler</a>, hng vt mt Juventus trong cuc ua chiu m ti nng tr ngi c.\r\n\r\n- PSG  a ra mc gi 20 triu euro hi mua hu v tri Layvin Kurzawa (Monaco)  thay th Lucas Digne.\r\n<div align="center"><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/13/8/digneliverpool.jpg" alt="Digne ang l mc tiu theo ui ca Liverpool" border="0px" />\r\nDigne ang l mc tiu theo ui ca Liverpool</div>\r\n- Theo Independent, M.U  t c tha thun chiu m trung v Nicolas Otamendi (Valencia).\r\n\r\n- Ngi i din Alessandro Canovi ca tin v Thiago Motta s gp g BL PSG  bn tho v tng lai ca cu th gc Brazil.\r\n\r\n- Cu cu th Arsenal, Emmanuel Eboue hin tht nghip v ang cn nhc chuyn ti thi u  gii Super League ca n  (ISL). Hin cu th ngi B Bin Ng ang nhn c li mi t 2 CLB FC Pune City v Mumbai City FC.\r\n\r\n- Bayer Leverkusen  hon tt bn hp ng tr gi 17,5 triu bng  chiu m tin v Charles Aranguiz t Internacional (Brazil).\r\n<div align="center"><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/13/8/charles_aranguiz.jpg" alt="Aranguiz ha hn s gip tuyn gia ca Leverkusen chi tt hn trong ma gii mi" border="0px" />\r\nAranguiz ha hn s gip tuyn gia ca Leverkusen chi tt hn trong ma gii mi</div>\r\n- Hu v Alvaro Arbeloa vn s tip tc gn b vi Real Madrid trong thi gian ti d anh  c West Ham v mt s CLB M lin h.\r\n\r\n- Sau Luis Nani v Robin van Persie, Fenerbahce ang ln k hoch chiu m thm mt thnh vin khc ca M.U l tin v Marouane Fellaini.\r\n\r\n- Tin o Raul Jimenez xc nhn anh s ri Atletico Madrid  gia nhp Benfica trong ngy hm nay (13/8).\r\n\r\n- HLV Rafa Benitez kh n tng vi mn trnh din ca tin o tr Marco Asensio trong giai on giao hu va qua nn quyt nh gi anh li thay v cho mn.\r\n\r\n- Tin o tr 18 tui Taiwo Awoniyi ca Kalmar FF (Thy in)  vt qua bui kim tra y t v k hp ng chuyn nghip vi Liverpool. Tuy vy, anh s c cho cc CLB  B v H Lan mn  tch ly kinh nghim.\r\n<div align="center"><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/13/8/awoniyi.jpg" alt="Awoniyi l mt trong nhng ti nng tr sng gi ca Nigeria" border="0px" />\r\nAwoniyi l mt trong nhng ti nng tr sng gi ca Nigeria\r\n<div align="left">- M.U bt ng a tin v tr 16 tui Reece Oxford ca West Ham vo tm ngm sau khi anh thi u n tng  trn thng Arsenal 2-0 ti vng 1 Ngoi hng Anh 2015/16.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n- CLB Sunderland va ng  mun mua tin v Mousa Dembele t Tottenham vi mc gi 15 triu bng.\r\n\r\n- Chn st 19 tui Antonio Sanabria  c Roma gi n Sporting Gijon theo dng cho mn di hn.\r\n\r\n- Tin o <a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/60/128519/dzeko-hoan-tat-thu-tuc-gia-nhap-roma.bdplus">Edin Dzeko ca Man City  hon tt vic chuyn ti thi u cho AS Roma</a> theo dng cho mn n cui ma, km iu khon mua t.\r\n\r\n- <a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/60/128549/southampton-chieu-mo-cau-thu-tu-chelsea.bdplus">Southampton xc nhn  chiu m thnh cng tin v Oriol Romeu</a>ca Chelsea vi gi 7,1 triu euro. Cu th 23 tui ngi Ty Ban Nha ny  k hp ng 3 nm vi Southampton.\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Tng hp chuyn nhng 13/8: Juve hi mua Ramires v Cuadrado', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tong-hop-chuyen-nhuong-138-juve-hoi-mua-ramires-va-cuadrado', '', '', '2015-08-14 21:56:25', '2015-08-14 14:56:25', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3831', 0, 'post', '', 0),
