(3850, 2, '2015-08-14 22:08:33', '2015-08-14 15:08:33', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">Trong lch s Bundesliga, cha i bng no ginh a bc 4 ma gii lin tip. Nhng th h  c lit vo hng huyn thoi ca Bayern hay Mgladbach cng u khng th bc qua li nguyn s 4.  chnh l th thch vi thy tr HLV Pep Guardiola...</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/10/bundesliga.jpg" alt="Pep Guardiola v hc tr s phi vt qua li nguyn s 4 nu cn mun c m a bc vo cui ma\r\n" />Pep Guardiola v hc tr s phi vt qua li nguyn s 4 nu cn mun c m a bc vo cui ma</div>\r\n<h2>QU KH NGNG NG</h2>\r\n<div>Trong lch s hn 50 nm tn ti ca Bundesliga,  c 5 ln c mt i bng v ch  3 ma lin tip. Ngoi tr thnh tch 3 ma v ch gn y ca Bayern th 4 ln trc  (3 ln Bayern, 1 ln Mgladbach), cc CLB u  phi dng chn  ma gii th 4.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Bayern  gii on hong kim trong nhng nm u thp nin 70 vi Sepp Meier, Franz Beckenbauer, Gerd Mueller...  3 nm v ch lin tip t 1972-1974. Nhng tng khng g c th cn ni tp th v i  th Mgladbach vi nhng Berti Vogts, Rainer Bonhof, Jupp Heynckes... xut hin. Th h ny ca HLV Udo Lattek khng ch ph th c tn ca Bayern m cn lp ra mt  ch mi vi 3 ma v ch lin tip trc khi bt ng b Cologne chn ng.  2 ln khc Hm xm tng v ch 3 ma lin tip l 1985-1987 v 1999-2001, h cng ln lt b Bremen ri Dortmund ngng ng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/26/bayernvshamburg4.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>C mt im chung trong c 4 ln m cc i bng b son ngi ny th h u l nhng ng vin sng gi nht trc ngy khai mn. Ngoi tr s sa st kh hiu ca Bayern  ma 1974/75, nhng ln cn li, cc i bng ny u nm trong nhm u nhng khng th v ch. Ma 1977/78, Mgladbach thm ch cn mt chc v ch vo tay Cologne ch bi v km i th khi xt hiu s. Nh vy, truyn thuyt v li nguyn s 4 l c tht.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Cng vi nhng m nh t lch s , thch thc Bayern ang phi i mt  ma gii mi cng khin NHM i bng x Bavaria lo lng. Khng kh  thy rng y l ma gii m HLV Pep Guardiola ang phi chu mt sc p khng khip.  khng ch l sc p v thnh tch, v li chi m cn c v nhng chi tit nh  hu trng m nu Pep x l khng kho c th khin tnh trng tc nc v b xy ra.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<h2>C HI GHI DANH</h2>\r\n<div>Nhng chng c c hi no khng i km vi nhng th thch, nht l nhng c hi mang tnh lch s nh thy tr Pep Guardiola ang c  pha trc. B li ng sau li nguyn t qu kh, nhng kh khn ang  dng... tim n th c th thy rng Bayern vn ang c c hi khng th tuyt vi hn  ghi danh vi s sch.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Xt v i hnh, khng i bng no c th b vi Bayern. D  bn Bastian Schweinsteiger cho Man United nhng Bayern  a v Arturo Vidal  thay th. Ngoi ra, Douglas Costa cng c xem l mt s b sung cht lng,   c th gip Hm xm bng n ngay c khi khng c Franck Ribery.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/26/bayernvshamburg2.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Cng phi thy rng, vic cc i bng  pha sau Bayern nh Wolfsburg, Dortmund, Mgladbach, Leverkusen hay Schalke u tng cng ng k  H ny chnh l mt li th na vi i bng x Bavaria. Bayern c th s gp kh khn hn trong nhng ln i u vi nhm 5 i th cng ca trn nhng n s gip cho Hm xm duy tr c s tp trung xuyn sut ma, iu m h khng c c  2 ma gii gn nht. Cha k, chnh cc i bng pha sau Bayern cng s ngng ng nhau. Khi , k nng v vt im s trc cc i th yu ca thy tr Pep Guardiola s c pht huy ti a.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Bundesliga l gii u ng trng, khng phi l th thc loi trc tip. Bayern c th sy chn  mt vi trn u nhng tht kh trng ch h ri vo khng hong bi h qu mnh so vi phn cn li. S l ng t nu Bayern khng v ch Bundesliga 2015/16, huyn thoi Lothar Matthaeus, ngi  d on ng kch bn ma gii trc nhn nh.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table width="" align="">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>Bayern vn nng k nht</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/26/bayernvshamburg5.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Cc nh ci gn nh treo ca Bayern v ch vi t l n cc thp, t 10, n 1.  nhm pha sau, Wolfsburg v Dortmund c nh gi ngang nhau trong khi  mc  thp hn l nhm Leverkusen, Mgladbach v Schalke.</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Khi tranh Bundesliga 2015/16: Bayern v li nguyn s 4', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'khoi-tranh-bundesliga-201516-bayern-va-loi-nguyen-so-4', '', '', '2015-08-14 23:37:21', '2015-08-14 16:37:21', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3850', 0, 'post', '', 0),
