(3854, 2, '2015-08-14 23:07:09', '2015-08-14 16:07:09', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">M.U ang hc theo Arsenal, em v mt tin o cnh ca Barcelona v bin anh ta thnh cu th tr ct. Kt qu ma gii va qua vi Alexis Sanchez l 20 bn thng cng danh hiu Cu th xut sc nht nm ca CLB.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/31/sanchezpedro14-8.jpg" alt="Pedro s tip bc ng i c Sanchez  ta sng  Ngoi hng Anh?" />Pedro s tip bc ng i c Sanchez  ta sng  Ngoi hng Anh?\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Nu nh Pedro Rodriguez cng ha nhp vi l M.U nhanh nh Sanchez  Arsenal, HLV Louis van Gaal s c ca tng l thin ti chuyn nhng. Nhng liu vin cnh ti p y c xy ra  Old Trafford?</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<h2>Li chi</h2>\r\n<div>Nhng con s thng k ch ra rng Sanchez v Pedro c kh nhiu im chung trong li chi. Ma gii 2011/12, nm u tin Sanchez khoc o Barcelona, anh ghi c 11 bn trong 20 ln xut pht, cn Pedro ghi 5 bn cng trong ngn y trn.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ma gii th hai, Sanchez ghi 8 bn trong 18 ln ra sn trong i hnh xut pht, cn Pedro ghi c 7 trong 23 trn. Ma 2013/14, tuyn th Chile ghi 19 bn trong 27 trn xut pht, tin o ngi Ty Ban Nha c c 15 ln lp cng sau 28 ln ra sn t u. T l ghi bn ca Sanchez n tng hn, nhng Pedro li gii kin to hn.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Sanchez l cu th thun chn phi thch i bng t cnh tri, cn Pedro thun c 2 chn v cng c li chi tng t. Tuy nhin, Sanchez li hn Pedro  ch c th chi c trung l. Anh c th hnh m, th lc tt  tc chin c lp. V tr tin o cm cng thuc v anh  T Chile, v thnh thong c b tr khi cn chi cho Barcelona.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/31/sanchezcutinside14-8.jpg" alt="C Sanchez v Pedro u thch khoan ph t cnh vo trung l ri dt im" border="0" /></div>\r\n<div>C Sanchez v Pedro u thch khoan ph t cnh vo trung l ri dt im</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Pedro, hay nh CV Barca vn thng gi l Pedrito, c th thi u nh mt s 9 o, thm ch Vicente Del Bosque cn tng th nghim anh  vai tr hu v cnh ti k World Cup 2014, nhng Luis Enrique li khng sn sng th nghim nhiu nh vy, d i lc Barcelona t ra thiu mt phng n d phng cho Dani Alves.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ngoi ra, Pedro cn h tr phng ng rt hiu qu, cng thm <a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/19/128516/ta-nghi-gi-khi-nghi-ve-pedro.bdplus">kh nng pressing n tng</a> nh Thierry Henry tng nhn xt. Sanchez s hu ngun nng lng v tn, nhng anh khng sn sng li su phng ng nh ngi ng i c  Nou Camp.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>iu m Sanchez c nhng Pedro khng c,  l kinh nghim thi u  mt i bng khc ngoi Barcelona. Arsene Wenger trc khi mua Sanchez chng bao gi phi t ra cu hi: Liu cu y c th chi tt bn ngoi Nou Camp?, bi tuyn th Chile  chng t c nng lc thi cn khoc o Udinese  Serie A.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Pedro gia nhp Barcelona C 1 thp k v trc t CLB San Isidro ca qun o Canary, v   t by n nay. Nhng bn cnh , Pedro c mt im ng  t tin,  l ngi ang ch anh  Old Trafford, HLV Louis van Gaal rt hiu anh. Tin o 28 tui cng  chi tt khi ln tuyn Ty Ban Nha, k c khi i bng ny khng chi theo phong cch Barcelona.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/31/pedro14-8.jpg" alt="Pedro cha tng chi bng nh cao  CLB no ngoi Barca" border="0" /></div>\r\n<div>Pedro cha tng chi bng nh cao  CLB no ngoi Barca</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<h2>Tnh cch</h2>\r\n<div>C kh nhiu im tng ng v tnh cch gia Sanchez v Pedro. Sanchez ch l mt ht ct gia v vn tn tui ln  Nou Camp, ch l mt g v danh nu so vi Lionel Messi, Xavi hay Andres Iniesta. <a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/19/128521/pedro-rodriguez-thien-than-bi-choi-bo.bdplus">Pedro cng rt khim nhng gia dn sao Barcelona</a>, d anh vn bit cch khin ngi ta nh ti mnh  nhng thi khc quan trng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>C mt cu chuyn t ngi bit,  l Del Bosque tng trao chic o s 2 cho Pedro  VCK World Cup 2010, sau khi tt c u t chi mang n. Tin o ca Barcelona chp nhn v chng h phn nn g, cho ti khi anh bn Fernando Torres ng ra ln ting h. Khi , Pedro mi c i o s 18.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Cng nh vy, d ta sng rc r  Emirates, chng ai ngh Sanchez s tr thnh th lnh ca Arsenal. Pedro n M.U cng vy, chc chn khng phi mt Eric Cantona khc.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/31/pedromessi14-8.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>Pedro lun sn sng nhng nh n sn khu cho ng i</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thay vo , c 2 u bit cch ta sng khi i bng cn ti h nht. Pedro c phn tri hn Sanchez  im ny. Anh thng xuyn l tc gi nhng bn quyt nh  trn cu ln. Thnh tch ca anh  cc trn chung kt l v cng n tng: Ghi bn trong 2 trn chung kt Siu cp chu u, 1 chung kt Cp Nh Vua, 1 chung kt Champions League, 1 chung kt Club World Cup v 2 chung kt Siu cp Ty Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Mt bt li vi Pedro  l nu nh Sanchez ti Arsenal v lp tc xc nh c v tr cng nh vai tr ca mnh trong mt h thng chin thut r rng, th Van Gaal c v cn m h vi nhng con ngi mi trong tay. Anh c l s  tin o cnh, nhng phi hay tri? Trong s  no? Chnh Van Gaal c l cng cha c p n.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<h2>Kt lun</h2>\r\n<div>Mua cu th t Barcelona lun mang ti kt qu tt p cho cc i bng gii Ngoi hng Anh trong nhiu nm gn y. Yaya Toure l nhn t ch cht trong 2 chc v ch ca Man City, Cesc Fabregas ha nhp nhanh nh th cha h ri xa x sng m ngay khi cp bn Chelsea v lp tc gip i bng ny ginh li ngi bu.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thm c trng hp ca Sanchez na, M.U  c tha c s  k vng vo mt <a class="news_ref" href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/59/128513/pedro-se-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-trong-48-gio-toi.bdplus">bn hp ng thnh cng vi Pedro</a>. Anh s chp nhn bt c vai tr no Van Gaal giao ph, v cng hin tn ty nh mt chin binh ngay c khi bit rng  Old Trafford, chng cn ci bng khng l no ca nhng Messi, Neymar hay Luis Suarez.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'M.U: Nhn Alexis Sanchez, thy nim tin  Pedro', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'm-u-nhin-alexis-sanchez-thay-niem-tin-o-pedro', '', '', '2015-08-14 23:07:09', '2015-08-14 16:07:09', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3854', 0, 'post', '', 0),
