, '', '', '2015-08-14 23:07:15', '2015-08-14 16:07:15', '', 3854, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/3854-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3857, 2, '2015-08-14 23:22:10', '2015-08-14 16:22:10', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary"><strong>Chelsea  khng n bt thnh cho th mn Thibaut Courtois, ng ngha vi vic th mn ngi B s vng mt  trn Super Sunday m Ch nht ti v c hi c trao cho Begovic.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"><strong></strong></div>\r\n<div class="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/7/zouma.jpg" alt="HLV Mourinho s a Zouma ln hng tin v  b sung cht thp?" />HLV Mourinho s a Zouma ln hng tin v  b sung cht thp?\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10">Th mn: Asmir Begovic</div>\r\n<div><a class="news_ref" href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/14/128230/courtois-chi-bi-treo-gio-tran-gap-man-city-o-vong-2-ngoai-hang-anh.bdplus">Chic th  ti hi ca Courtois trong trn ha 2-2 trc Swansea</a>  vng u m mn  to c hi cho Begovic c ra sn v th hin ti nng  trn u tm im vng 2 Ngoi hng Anh.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Hu v tri: Cesar Azpilicueta</div>\r\n<div>D thi u khng thc s tt  trn m mn ma gii, nhng s cnh tranh bn hnh lang tri ca Chelsea l khng nhiu v th nhiu kh nng Azpilicueta vn c HLV Jose Mourinho s dng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Trung v: John Terry</div>\r\n<div>L i trng, th lnh tinh thn ca Chelsea, vic Terry c mt trong i hnh chnh l iu khng phi bn ci.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/41/terry.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>John Terry vn l linh hn ca Chelsea</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Trung v: Gary Cahill</div>\r\n<div>Li chi ln x, s n  tuyt vi vi Terry cng kinh nghim trn mc gip Cahill c nh gi cao hn n em Kurt Zouma v vic c mt trong i hnh ra sn l iu d hiu.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Hu v phi: Branislav Ivanovic</div>\r\n<div>Khng cn l mt Ivanovic dng mnh nh ma gii trc, cu th 31 tui ang dn bc quan bn kia sn dc ca s nghip. Tuy nhin, kinh nghim cng nh bn lnh trn mc ca Ivanovic vn rt cn thit vi Chelsea  nhng trn u quan trng nh th ny.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Tin v trung tm: Kurt Zouma</div>\r\n<div>Vi tnh cht quan trng ca trn u, rt c th HLV Mourinho s tr li phong cch "dng xe but" s trng ca mnh. Ma gii trc, ng tng nhiu ln s dng Zouma  v tr tin v nh chn,  ngay pha trn b i trung v mi khi gp cc i bng ln. Nhiu kh nng kch bn ny s ti din trong trn u vi Man City, ng ngha Fabregas s c y cao ln  h cng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/41/xouma.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>Zouma s l nhn t b n ca Chelsea  trn u vi Man City?</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Tin v trung tm: Nemanja Matic</div>\r\n<div>Khng qu khi ni Matic l l phi ca Chelsea. S vng mt ca tuyn th Serbia lun khin Chelsea gp nguy trong vic phng ng t xa, v th Matic s l la chn hng u ca HLV Mourinho  v tr tin v trung tm.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Tin v cnh phi: Willian</div>\r\n<div>Li chi nng n, nhit tnh l im mnh ca Willian, chnh iu ny gip tuyn th Brazil lun l u tin hng u trong i hnh ra sn ca Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Tin v cnh tri: Eden Hazard</div>\r\n<div>Ch c chn thng hay th pht mi ngn cn Hazard khng c tn trong i hnh ra sn ca Chelsea.  trn u quan trng vi Man City, cu th xut sc nht gii Ngoi hng Anh ma trc c k vng s ta sng v mang v chin thng cho i nh.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/41/hazard.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>Hazard l nim hy vng ln ca Chelsea  trn i chin vi Man City</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Tin v cng: Cesc Fabregas</div>\r\n<div>Cng vi Terry, Matic v Hazard, Fabregas l cu th khng th ng n ti Chelsea. D cha ly li c phong  cao nht, nhng Fabregas vn s l la chn hng u trong i hnh ra sn, nht l  trn u quan trng nh th ny.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Tin o: Diego Costa</div>\r\n<div>Hng cng Chelsea c s gp mt ca 3 tin o hng u l Diego Costa, Radamel Falcao, Loic Remy.  la chn, c l Diego Costa vn l u tin hng u, d tuyn th Ty Ban Nha cha c c phong  tt nht. y cng l iu d hiu, bi <a class="news_ref" href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/14/127725/goc-nhin-falcao-chelsea-chi-khac-falcao-m-u-o-kieu-toc.bdplus">Falcao vn th hin b mt bc nhc ging nh thi cn khoc o M.U</a> trong khi Remy c l ch thch hp vi vai ngi ng th.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/41/doihinhchelsea.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>i hnh d kin ca Chelsea  trn Super Sunday vi Man City</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'i hnh d kin Chelsea gp Man City: Zouma  tin v phng ng?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'doi-hinh-du-kien-chelsea-gap-man-city-zouma-da-tien-ve-phong-ngu', '', '', '2015-08-14 23:22:10', '2015-08-14 16:22:10', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3857', 0, 'post', '', 0),
