98/99, Real Madrid cng khai tuyn b rt hm m Anelka v mun c s phc v ca cu th ngi Php. p li, Anelka cng mun ti Ty Ban Nha thi u khi th hin thi  thi u h hng. Thi im , truyn thng cng t cho Anelka bit danh "Ngi Php hn di".</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/41/anelka.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Kt qu: Arsenal buc phi bn Anelka cho Real vi mc ph 22,3 triu bng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>3. Pierre Van Hooijdonk (Nottingham sang Vitesse)</div>\r\n<div>Gp cng ln gip Nottingham Forest thng hng Premier League 1998/1999, song Van Hooijdonk tht vng vi BL i bng v khng chu tng cng lc lng. Chnh iu ny anh  t chi k hp ng v lin tc i ra i, nhng khng c chp nhn. Van Hooijdonk sau  t chi ra sn thi u cng nh tham gia tp luyn, thm ch cn khng n mng bn thng cng cc ng i.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/41/hooijdonk.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Kt qu: Nm 1999,Van Hooijdonk tr li i bng qu nh, Vitesse vi mc ph 3,5 triu bng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>4. Robbie Savage (Birmingham sang Blackburn)</div>\r\n<div>Thng 1/2005, Savage  np n ln BL Birmingham vi mong mun c chuyn sang Blackburn  c gn cha m  Wrexham, bt chp khong cch t Birmingham ti Wrexham gn hn so vi Blackburn. Thi im , Ch tch David Sullivan  v cng tc gin v khng chp nhn cho anh ra i.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/41/savange.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Kt qu: Savage tha nhn anh  khng c gng trong trn u cui cng ca mnh ti Birmingham vi Newcastle. Sau , Savage c bn cho Blackburn vi mc ph 3 triu bng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>5. Dimitar Berbatov (Tottenham sang M.U)</div>\r\n<div>Trc s quan tm ca M.U, Berbatov  b phn tm d mi tri qua mt ma gii 2007/08 thnh cng trong mu o Tottenham. Trong bi cnh Robbie Keane, i tc n  b bn sang Liverpool, Berbatov cng cng khai i ra i nhng khng c BL chp nhn. Tuyn th Bulgaria vn tip tc  li sn White Hart Lane, song tm tr v nhit huyt li khng cn khin phong  st gim.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/41/berbatov.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Kt qu: Berbatov chuyn ti M.U  ngy cui ca k chuyn nhng (1/9/2008) vi mc ph 30,75 triu bng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>6. William Gallas (Chelsea sang Arsenal)</div>\r\n<div>Khng c BL Chelsea ng  k hp ng di hn v khng c thi u  v tr trung v yu thch (b y ra cnh tri), Gallas  nh cng v yu cu c ra i thi im trc khi World Cup 2006 khi tranh.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/41/gallas.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Kt qu: Arsenal v Chelsea thc hin vic trao i cu th gia Gallas v Ashley Cole.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>7. Peter Odemwingie (West Brom sang Cardiff)</div>\r\n<div>Thng 1/2013, tin o Odemwingie  khin lng bng  Anh git mnh khi t chi thi u cho West Brom, ng thi li  t ti i bn doanh ca CLB QPR  m phn hp ng v kim tra sc khe. Tuy nhin, do 2 i cha thng nht mc ph nn thng v ny b  b v tin o ngi Nam Phi phi tr li sn The Hawthorns thi u phn cn li ca ma gii.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/41/odemwingie.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Kt qu: Cui ma gii, West Brom bn Odemwingie cho Cardiff vi mc ph 2,25 triu bng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>8. Clint Dempsey (Fulham sang Tottenham)</div>\r\n<div>Nm 2012, Dempsey  nh cng ti Fulham vi mong mun c chuyn sang Liverpool thi u. Tuy nhin, cuc cch mng ca HLV Brendan Rodgers thi im  khng c ch cu th ngi M .</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/41/dempsey.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Kt qu: Dempsey b BL Fulham bn cho Tottenham vo ngy cui cng ca k chuyn nhng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>9. Carlos Tevez (Man City sang Juventus)</div>\r\n<div>Ch vi ngy sau khi gip Man City ginh danh hiu FA Cup, Tevez  i ra i  chuyn sang Italia khoc o Juventus. Ngi sao ngi Argentina thi im  khng tr li thnh Manchester sau k ngh H, nhng trc thi  kin quyt ca BL i bng, Tevez vn phi  li sn Etihad. Nhng mi quan h cng thng khng chu dng li khi Tevez t chi ra sn trong trn u ti Champions League vi Bayern Munich, ng thi b v qu nh Argentina ... chi golf.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/41/tevez.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Kt qu: Tevez b pht tin v nhng hnh ng  v tr li Man City vo thng 2 v thi u nt phn cn li ca ma gii, ln ngi v ch gii Ngoi hng Anh ma 2011/12 trc khi chuyn sang Juventus.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>10. Luis Suarez (Liverpool sang Barca)</div>\r\n<div>Thng 5/2013, Luis Suarez cho bit mun c chia tay Liverpool, vi l do cc phng tin truyn thng xm phm qu nhiu vo cuc sng c nhn. Thi im , Arsenal tng nh  c s phc v ca Suarez khi b ra 40 triu + 1 bng  chiu m anh nhng bt thnh. Rt cuc cu th ngi Uruguay  li thm mt ma gii v tr thnh Vua ph li gii Ngoi hng Anh vi 31 bn thng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/14/41/suarez.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Kt qu: Sau 1 ma gii yu cu c ra i, Suarez chuyn sang Barca ma H nm 2014 vi mc ph 75 triu bng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'De Gea, Sterling, Suarez v nhng v nh cng i ra i', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3865-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-14 23:39:19', '2015-08-14 16:39:19', '', 3865, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/3865-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
