(3894, 2, '2015-08-15 21:19:12', '2015-08-15 14:19:12', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">Sau mt ma gii bt bt, Dortmund ang rt quyt tm tm li v th  Bundesliga. V dn mt k ni lon Mgladbach bng mt trn thng trong ngy ra qun s l li tuyn b anh thp nht ca thy tr HLV Thomas Tuchel cho quyt tm v tham vng y.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/50/view-dortmund_593c.jpg" alt="Marco Reus (gia) v cc ngi sao tn cng s gip Dortmund ginh chin thng" />Marco Reus (gia) v cc ngi sao tn cng s gip Dortmund ginh chin thng\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Ma gii 2014/15 tht bi   hon ton pha sau lng. Trc mt Dortmund hin l ma gii mi vi rt nhiu hy vng cng tn HLV trng Thomas Tuchel.  l nhng hy vng rt... thc t sau nhng g i bng vng Ruhr  th hin trong H qua.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Dortmund di s dn dt ca Tuchel l mt tp th chi linh hot. Nhng im mnh nht ca Dortmund di thi Juergen Klopp vn c Tuchel duy tr.  l li chi pressing kh chu v nhng ming n phn cng sc lm, iu  c cc cu th Dortmund ph din trong chin thng 2-0 trc Juventus  trn giao hu H qua. Nhng Dortmund ca Tuchel khng ch bit mi pressing. H cho thy cng c th bng n vi li chi tn cng p t th trn m chin thng 5-0 trc Wolfsberger  lt v vng loi th 3 Europa League  chng mnh iu .</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>im nhn ca Tuchel trong nhng ngy u tin  Dortmund l vic tin tng vo cc tn binh v lm hi sinh nhng gi tr c. Th thnh Roman Burki c tin tng thay lo tng Weidenfeller, tin v tr Julian Weigl cng c la chn thay Sven Bender hay tn binh Gonzalo Castro cng c giao nhng nhim v quan trng. Nhng ng k nht phi l vic Tuchel  lm hi sinh ngi sao t gi nht lch s i bng Henrikh Mkhitaryan. Cu th tng b b qun  ma trc nay  gp du giy vo 7 bn thng trong 4 trn u tin ca Dortmund, trong  c 4 ln lp cng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>S tr li ca Mkhitaryan gip Dortmund c c b ba tn cng ng  mi hng th ti Bundesliga phi khip s gm Reus - Aubameyang - Mkhitaryan. y l b 3 va c c tc  ln k thut, c kh nng phi hp vi nhau  tc  cao. Vic Aubameyang ang ngy mt sc bn hn  v tr trung phong cm cng khin sc cng ph ca mi inh ba ny tr nn ng s hn.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Vi s chun b k lng v vic ang c phong  cao, Dortmund chc chn khng h ngn Mgladbach d y l i bng  cn ch  v tr th 3 ma trc. Vi li chi kh tng ng, trn u ny ha hn s rt cng thng  khu trung tuyn. Tuy nhin, so vi Mgladbach th Dortmund c nh gi cao  kh nng bng n trong li chi v h s tn dng c li th ny  ginh chin thng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I HNH D KIN</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>Dortmund: Burki; Piszczek, Sokratis, Hummels, Schmelzer; Weigl; Reus, Guendogan, Castro, Mkhitaryan; Aubameyang.</div>\r\n<div>Mgladbach: Sommer; Jantschke, Schulz, Christensen, Wendt; Stindl, Xhaka; Traore, Herrmann; Raffael; Drmic.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>C BIT</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>6 ln tip n Mgladbach trn sn nh gn y, Dortmund thng theo chu  5 trn.</div>\r\n<div>4/6 trn gn y gia hai i ti Signal Iduna Park c t 3 bn tr ln.</div>\r\n<div>Dortmund thng theo chu   4/5 trn sn nh gn y.</div>\r\n<div>9/13 trn gn y ca Dortmund c t 3 bn thng tr ln.</div>\r\n<div>Trong 86 trn i u gia 2 i,  c tng cng 283 bn thng c ghi (trung bnh 3,3 bn/trn).</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>C BIT</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>t nht 1 bn hip 1: 11/12 trn gn y gia hai i ti Signal Iduna Park c bn thng trong hip 1. Tng t, 16/17 trn gn y ca Dortmund c bn thng trong 45 pht u. Trn ny kh c ngoi l.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>D ON: 3-1</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>BN CHN T S NO?</div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/50/dortmund.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Nhn nh Dortmund vs Mgladbach, 23h30 ngy 15/8', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nhan-dinh-dortmund-vs-mgladbach-23h30-ngay-158', '', '', '2015-08-15 21:19:12', '2015-08-15 14:19:12', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3894', 0, 'post'