(3897, 2, '2015-08-15 21:22:44', '2015-08-15 14:22:44', '<div id="ContentBindr" class="contentview">\r\n<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">Bayer Leverkusen tip Hoffenheim trong s t tin cao  trn hng cng. Cc hc tr ca HLV Roger Schmidt  ghi ti 10 bn trong 3 trn thng lin tip va qua (2 giao hu, 1 ti Cp Quc gia).</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/50/view-leverkusen_400c.jpg" alt="Cc chn st Leverkusen (o sm) ang t im ri phong " />Cc chn st Leverkusen (o sm) ang t im ri phong </div>\r\n<div>iu lm HLV Schmidt hi lng nht l phong  bng n ca Stefan Kiessling khi tin o s mt ca Leverkusen lin tc pht ha 3 trn gn y. Nhng v tinh xung quanh Kiessling nh Mehmedi, Son, Bellarabi cng c nhng mn trnh din thuyt phc.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Trong khi Leverkusen t im ri phong  ngay trc vch xut pht th ngc li, Hoffenheim khng c s chun b tt. on qun ca HLV Markus Gisdol va  thua b bng 0-2 trc i th hng Nh 1860 Munich ti vng 1 Cp Quc gia c. Vi phong  thm hi ny, Hoffenheim kh lng tr vng ti cho la BayArena ca Leverkusen. Cng cn nhn mnh rng Leverkusen thng ti 12 trong 14 ln chm trn gn y vi i th min Ty Nam nc c.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ngoi ra, sn nh cng l u th v cng ln ca thy tr HLV Roger Schmidt khi h ton thng c 6 trn gn y ti BayArena, trong khun kh Bundesliga. Tt c  sn sng cho ngy ra qun trn y hng khi v thnh cng ca i bng xp th 4 Bundesliga ma trc.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I HNH D KIN</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>Leverkusen: Leno, Hilbert, Tah, K.Papadopoulos, Wendell, L.Bender, Kramer, Bellarabi, Son, Mehmedi, Kiessling.</div>\r\n<div>Hoffenheim: Baumann, Kaderabek, Suele, Schaer, Kim, Schwegler, Polanski, Schmid, Volland, Zuber, Uth.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>C BIT</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>Hip 1 ti a 1 bn: 5/8 ln i u gn y gia Leverkusen v Hoffenheim chng kin ti a 1 bn thng trong 4