(3900, 2, '2015-08-15 21:27:47', '2015-08-15 14:27:47', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">Nm 2009, khi ang chy ua tr li gh ch tch Real Madrid, mt trong nhng cu slogan ca Florentino Perez l ch dnh 1 nm  mua s tn binh cho 3 nm. Perez  lm ng nh vy v  nm th 7 ca nhim k 2, ng khng cn nhu cu t tin na.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/51/real6.jpg" alt="Benitez v Ch tch Perez" />Benitez v Ch tch Perez\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>MA H THIU LA</h2>\r\n<div>Ma H ny, Los Blancos  ln lt t chn ti Australia, Trung Quc, c v Na Uy, nhng c v nh quyn sc ca h th vn  li  Madrid. V d  chi tng cng 52 triu euro cho 6 tn binh, nhng khng ci tn no trong s   sc nng  khin cc Madridista phi nhng my. Khng k Marco Asensio c tnh vo ma trc, h ch a v Kiko Casilla (6 triu euro), Casemiro (7,5), Lucas Vazquez (1) v mi nht l Jesus Vallejo (6).</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Khng ai trong s ny xng ng c coi l ngi sao. V thm ch, ngay c bn hp ng ln nht tr gi 31,5 triu euro l Danilo cng ch c mt bui ra mt y t nht ngy hi u thng 7 trc khong 600 Madridista, <a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/59/112652/real-san-sang-mua-de-gea-voi-gia-ky-luc.bdplus">nhng ngi thc t ch tn dng c hi c mt  gi tn... David de Gea</a>. Nhng nu ngi Madrid khng chiu m c th thnh ny, Danilo s l Galactico ca ma H 2015. ng l  lu lm ri, Bernabeu mi li qunh hiu n th trong mt k chuyn nhng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/51/real7.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>David de Gea l th thnh m Real Madrid ang mun c</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thc t ny qu l k l. V thng sau mi ma gii trng tay, Real Madrid s li in cung nhy vo mua sm. S xut hin ca mt HLV mi, ngoi vic em li mt trit l bng  mi, lun i km vi nhng con ngi mi. Tuy vy, en cho Rafael Benitez l hin ti, c v nh ch tch Perez li khng my mn m vi vic chi tin.</div>\r\n<h2>\r\nCY KO CA PEREZ</h2>\r\n<div>S d ni vy l k t khi tr li <a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/19/122335/florentino-perez-ke-doc-tai-o-bernabeu.bdplus">chic gh quyn lc nht  Bernabeu</a>, ng trm xy dng vn lun to iu kin ti a cho cc HLV. Ma H 2009, Perez  chi tng cng 257,4 triu euro  nht vo tay HLV Manuel Pellegrini mt lc 8 tn binh tn tui gm Cristiano Ronaldo, Kaka, Karim Benzema, Xabi Alonso, Raul Albiol, Alvaro Negredo, Esteban Granero v Alvaro Arbeloa. Ch sau  1 nm, l 93 triu euro cho 6 ci tn khc  ma u tin ca Jose Mourinho (2010/11).</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/51/real8.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>Nhng th m Benitez nhn c  ma u tin ti Real Madrid qu l ng ti thn</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ma H 2013, Carlo Ancelotti c cho n ti Bernabeu bng nhng tn binh sng gi nh Gareth Bale, Isco, Asier Illarramendi, Dani Carvajal v Casemiro. Mt nm sau, Perez li mang v cho Carletto thm 2 tn binh sng gi na l Toni Kroos v James Rodriguez. Tng cng, ng  chi 181,5 triu euro trong giai on 3 ma gn b vi Mourinho, v 302 triu euro trong 2 ma vi Ancelotti. So vi 2 con s trn, nhng g<a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/19/123167/6-van-de-benitez-phai-doi-mat-tai-real-madrid.bdplus">Benitez nhn c  ma u tin dn dt Real Madrid</a> qu l ng ti thn.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>L gii cho iu , Perez vn bo lu quan im mua 1 ma  dng cho 3 ma v mua t nhng cht. Tuy nhin, nh v von ca t Marca, nhng g ng lm li khin tt c khng khi ngh n hnh nh mnh ang cm mt cy ko, v c gng ct xn ngn sch chuyn nhng ca Real Madrid sau nhiu ma bo chi. M mt khi nh vy, Benitez c l ch c th t trch mnh khi chn khng ng thi im  tr v.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>TNH HNH MUA SM CA REALDI TRIU I CH TCH PEREZ</div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/51/real1.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>CON S</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>56 Theo cuc kho st mi y ca t AS, Keylor Navas (nh) ang c nh gi cao hn Kiko Casilla cho vai tr th thnh s 1 ca Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div>Th mn ngi Costa Rica c 56% s c gi bnh chn, Casilla l 43% v ch c 1% chn th thnh tr Ruben Yanez.</div>\r\n<div>Trn thc t, HLV Rafa Benitez cng  chm Navas cho vai tr ny,  ma gii bn l trc khi David de Gea cp bn Bernabeu vo ma H ti.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/51/real4.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Real Madrid mi chi 52 triu Euro trong h 2015: Vn en ca Benitez', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'real-madrid-moi-chi-52-trieu-euro-trong-he-2015-van-den-cua-benitez', '', '', '2015-08-15 21:27:47', '2015-08-15 14:27:47', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3900', 0, 'post', '', 0),
