 m vi vic chi tin.</div>\r\n<h2>\r\nCY KO CA PEREZ</h2>\r\n<div>S d ni vy l k t khi tr li <a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/19/122335/florentino-perez-ke-doc-tai-o-bernabeu.bdplus">chic gh quyn lc nht  Bernabeu</a>, ng trm xy dng vn lun to iu kin ti a cho cc HLV. Ma H 2009, Perez  chi tng cng 257,4 triu euro  nht vo tay HLV Manuel Pellegrini mt lc 8 tn binh tn tui gm Cristiano Ronaldo, Kaka, Karim Benzema, Xabi Alonso, Raul Albiol, Alvaro Negredo, Esteban Granero v Alvaro Arbeloa. Ch sau  1 nm, l 93 triu euro cho 6 ci tn khc  ma u tin ca Jose Mourinho (2010/11).</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/51/real8.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>Nhng th m Benitez nhn c  ma u tin ti Real Madrid qu l ng ti thn</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ma H 2013, Carlo Ancelotti c cho n ti Bernabeu bng nhng tn binh sng gi nh Gareth Bale, Isco, Asier Illarramendi, Dani Carvajal v Casemiro. Mt nm sau, Perez li mang v cho Carletto thm 2 tn binh sng gi na l Toni Kroos v James Rodriguez. Tng cng, ng  chi 181,5 triu euro trong giai on 3 ma gn b vi Mourinho, v 302 triu euro trong 2 ma vi Ancelotti. So vi 2 con s trn, nhng g<a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/19/123167/6-van-de-benitez-phai-doi-mat-tai-real-madrid.bdplus">Benitez nhn c  ma u tin dn dt Real Madrid</a> qu l ng ti thn.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>L gii cho iu , Perez vn bo lu quan im mua 1 ma  dng cho 3 ma v mua t nhng cht. Tuy nhin, nh v von ca t Marca, nhng g ng lm li khin tt c khng khi ngh n hnh nh mnh ang cm mt cy ko, v c gng ct xn ngn sch chuyn nhng ca Real Madrid sau nhiu ma bo chi. M mt khi nh vy, Benitez c l ch c th t trch mnh khi chn khng ng thi im  tr v.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>TNH HNH MUA SM CA REALDI TRIU I CH TCH PEREZ</div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/51/real1.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>CON S</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>56 Theo cuc kho st mi y ca t AS, Keylor Navas (nh) ang c nh gi cao hn Kiko Casilla cho vai tr th thnh s 1 ca Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div>Th mn ngi Costa Rica c 56% s c gi bnh chn, Casilla l 43% v ch c 1% chn th thnh tr Ruben Yanez.</div>\r\n<div>Trn thc t, HLV Rafa Benitez cng  chm Navas cho vai tr ny,  ma gii bn l trc khi David de Gea cp bn Bernabeu vo ma H ti.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/51/real4.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Real Madrid mi chi 52 triu Euro trong h 2015: Vn en ca Benitez', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3900-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-15 21:27:47', '2015-08-15 14:27:47', '', 3900, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/3900-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3903, 2, '2015-08-15 21:29:50', '2015-08-15 14:29:50', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">D  thua i ch nh Athletic Bilbao ti 0-4  lt i Siu cp Ty Ban Nha, HLV Luis Enrique vn tin tng Barcelona c th ngc dng ginh chin thng trn sn nh vo ngy 18/8.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox">\r\n<div class="mediaitem"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/8/barca_thua_bilbao.jpg" alt="S tht vng ca cc thnh vin Barca" /></div>\r\nS tht vng ca cc thnh vin Barca\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nSiu phm ca tin v San Jose (pht 13) v c hat-trick ca tin o Aritz Aduriz (53'', 62'', 68'')  gip <a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/19/128689/barcelona-thuc-thu-0-4-truoc-bilbao-trong-ngay-aduriz-lap-hat-trick.bdplus">Athletic Bilbao bt ng ginh chin thng m  4-0 trc Barcelona</a>  lt i Siu cp Ty Ban Nha.\r\n\r\nTr li phng vn sau trn, HLV Luis Enrique ca Barcelona tha nhn, th lc ca cc hc tr b bo mn sau trn Siu cp chu u kch tnh vi Sevilla (thng 5-4) l l do ng buc phi xoay tua i hnh.\r\n\r\nTi buc phi c nhng s thay i v chng ti ch c 3 ngy  hi phc sau trn u ti Tbilisi. Ti xin nhn trch nhim v trn thua ny", HLV Enrique qu quyt. "Thc s lch thi u  lm kh cho Barca, chng ti ch va mi tr v t Gruzia m thi. Nhng y khng phi thi gian than trch v lch thi u  ln t trc ri".\r\n<div align="center"><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/8/bilbaobarrca7.jpg" alt="Suarez v cc ng i  th tn dng cc c hi c c  sn San Mames" border="0px" />\r\nSuarez v cc ng i  khng th tn dng cc c hi c c  sn San Mames\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nNi v trn thua trc Bilbao, HLV Enrique tha nhn: Khng bao gi l d dng khi i u mt i bng nh Bilbao. Ti xin chc mng h, nhng ti th Hai ti (thi im din ra trn lt v) s l mt bu khng kh hon ton khc ti Nou Camp. Li ngc dng ? y mi ch l lt i v nu c i bng no c th li ngc dng th  chnh l Barca".\r\n\r\nTh qun Andres Iniesa ca Barca cng lc quan khi cho rng i bng x Catalan vn c th ginh c "c n 6": "Chng ti  phi tr gi cho sai lm ca mnh. Ton i  thi u khng tt trong ngy hm nay. Ti bit  ngc dng l rt kh khn nhng chng ti s c gng ht sc. Mi chuyn u c th xy ra".\r\n\r\nChn st Aritz Aduriz pha Bilbao ho hng chia s: "Ton i rt hi lng v chin thng ny. Chng ti hiu rng  c th nh bi Barca lun l iu rt kh khn. Vic Bilbao ghi c 4 bn vo li h trong trn u va qua l rt kh tin. Trc mt chng ti vn cn trn lt v v Bilbao vn rt thn trng v trong bng  khng th ni trc iu g.\r\n<div align="center"><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/8/bilbaobarrca9.jpg" alt="Aduriz v cc ng i t tin trc chuyn hnh qun n Nou Camp" border="0px" />\r\nAduriz v cc ng i t tin trc chuyn hnh qun n Nou Camp\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nChung cm xc vi Aduriz cn c ng thy Ernesto Valverde: y l mt m k diu  San Mames. Mt chin thng m trc Barca l v cng n tng bi v h rt him khi b thng li 4 bn. Tuy nhin vn cn trn lt v v chng ti phi ch n hm th Hai  bit mnh c th ginh Siu cp Ty Ban Nha hay khng. Trc mt, Bilbao vn cn nhiu vic phi lm v chng ti bit iu g ang ch i mnh  Nou Camp".\r\n\r\n"Cuc u  cn bng hn trc m nay, v chng ti  thng. Chc chn Bilbao s gp nhiu kh khn  trn u sp ti. Tt c cha c g m bo bi Barca c kh nng lm c mi th", HLV Valverde rt thn trng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'HLV Enrique vn t tin Barca s ngc dng trc Bilbao', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hlv-enrique-van-tu-tin-barca-se-nguoc-dong-truoc-bilbao', '', '', '2015-08-15 21:29:50', '2015-08-15 14:29:50', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3903', 0, 'post', '', 0),
