bng x Catalan khi y l Llorenc Serra Ferrer.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<h2>Ter Stegen   thng li bng na s bn thua c ma trc</h2>\r\n<div>Marc-Andre Ter Stegen   lt li 8 bn k t u ma, bng na s bn thua anh phi nhn sut c ma gii trc.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>D sao cng kh trch th thnh ngi c, bi ngoi tr bn thng m t s ca Mikel San Jose  trn thua Athletic Bilbao, 3 bn cn li u do li hng th hn l sai lm c nhn anh.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ma gii 2014/15, Ter Stegen  chi v cng n tng  Cp Nh Vua v Champions League vi 16 ln  thng li. ng tic l ngay  2 trn u ca ma 2015/16, anh  phi vo li nht bng ti mt na con s y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2 trn thua 8 bn, sau 14 nm Barca mi li t n th', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3906-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-15 21:31:32', '2015-08-15 14:31:32', '', 3906, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/3906-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3909, 2, '2015-08-15 21:33:08', '2015-08-15 14:33:08', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">Cc tin o ngi Ty Ban Nha ang c xu hng tm ng tr li La Liga. Sau Negredo, Torres v mi nht l Soldado l nhng a con lu lc  tr v. Nguyn nhn ca nhng s tr li ny bt ngun t s km thch nghi ca h khi ra nc ngoi thi u.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/50/anh-1.jpg" alt="Hng lot tin o ni ting Ty Ban Nha  v sp hi hng  tm li chnh mnh" />Hng lot tin o ni ting Ty Ban Nha  v sp hi hng  tm li chnh mnh\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>T CHUYN CA SOLDADO</div>\r\n<div>Cnh ca sn White Hart Lane  ng sp vi tin o Roberto Soldado. Sau 2 nm gia nhp Tottenham, tuyn th Ty Ban Nha ny  b tng i mt cch khng thng tic.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>m qua, i bng Anh  c mt thng bo ngn gn trn mng x hi Twitter xc nhn vic bn Soldado cho Villarreal. Chng ti  t c tha thun bn Soldado cho Villarreal. Chc cu y nhng iu tt p nht, l on tin xc nhn ca Tottenham trn Twitter chnh thc ca i bng. Ph chuyn nhng ca Soldado khng c tit l. Song, theo gii tho tin, n ri vo khong 10 triu bng, km xa so vi khon tin 26 triu bng m Tottenham  chi ra  a chn st ny sang Anh chi bng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>V con s 10 triu bng    ni ln s tht bi ca Soldado  White Hart Lane. Tuyn th Ty Ban Nha c Tottenham mua v t Valencia ma H nm 2013 vi s k vng rt ln. Khi , Spurs  phi chi ti 26 triu bng cho Valencia  c c s phc v ca Soldado, qua  bin anh thnh mt trong nhng cu th t gi nht trong lch s CLB.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/50/anh-2.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>Fernando Llorente</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Tng thi u rt n tng trong mu o ca Valencia v c xem l tng lai ca hng cng T Ty Ban Nha, nhng Soldado  khng thch nghi c vi mi trng bng  Anh. D c to iu kin ra sn kh thng xuyn, nhng anh t ra rt km n tng v ch ghi c vn vn 16 bn thng cho Tottenham trn mi mt trn, trong  c 5 bn  ma gii trc.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div> N NHNG S TR V BT C D KHC</div>\r\n<div>Trc khi Soldado tr v Ty Ban Nha  hon tt th tc chuyn sang thi u cho Villarreal, mt ng i khc ca anh  TQG cng c cho l  t c tha thun tr li La Liga thi u cho Sevilla.  l tin o Fernando Llorente ca Juventus.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/50/anh-3.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>Fernando Torres</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>D c thnh tch kh hn Soldado i cht, nhng Llorente cng khng gt hi c thnh cng khi ra nc ngoi thi u.  Juventus, anh cng ch l mt cu th siu d b v n nay mi ch ghi c tng cng 27 bn thng trong mu o i KV Serie A.</div>\r\n<div>Rt c th ch trong vi ngy ti, Soldado v Llorente s ni tip nhng ngi ng i nh Fernando Torres hay Alvaro Negredo tr v La Liga. im chung ca tt c nhng chn st ny l h u hi hng  th ci u. Trong , Torres cn b Chelsea tng sang Atletico  i bng th  Madrid gnh h h khon tin lng cao ngt ngng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>R rng, d T Ty Ban Nha  gt hi c rt nhiu thnh cng trong vng 1 thp k va qua, nhng cc tin o ca h li khng gy dng c danh ting khi ri qu hng. H t ra km thch nghi khi ra nc ngoi thi u v sau  u bng cch ny hay cch khc phi tm ng hi hng.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/50/anh-4.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>Alvaro Negredo</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>C th  cp n mt vi ci tn ng ch  khc  phi tr li La Liga trong ni  ch, ng k l trng hp ca tin o Rodrigo trong mu o Valencia hin nay.</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grd3">\r\n<div id="boxRgtNews">\r\n<div class="news_rel">\r\n<h6 class="tit">TIN LIN QUAN</h6>\r\n<ul class="newset lst">\r\n	<li class="fst"><a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/19/128710/hlv-enrique-van-tu-tin-barca-se-nguoc-dong-truoc-bilbao.bdplus"><img class="thumb10" src="http://stati