(3918, 2, '2015-08-15 22:02:25', '2015-08-15 15:02:25', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">D tng lai ca David de Gea ti M.U ang kh m mt, nhng HLV Louis van Gaal mi y vn ng k th mn ngi Ty Ban Nha vo danh sch tham d vng play-off Champions League.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/12/41/degea.jpg" alt="De Gea c ng k d Champions League" />De Gea c ng k d Champions League\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Gia tun ti M.U s c trn u vi Club Brugge (B) ti vng play-off Champions League.  chun b cho trn u ny, HLV Louis van Gaal  cng b danh sch cc cu th s tham d. ng ch , th thnh David de Gea vn c tn d rng tng lai ca anh ti sn Old Trafford ang l du hi ln.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Trc , ti trn khai mc gii Ngoi hng Anh ma 2015/16, HLV <a class="news_ref" href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/14/128075/de-gea-bi-gach-ten-khoi-tran-mo-man-ngoai-hang-anh.bdplus">Van Gaal  gch tn De Gea khi i hnh</a> v  Sergio Romero bt chnh. V th,  c nhiu ngun tin cho rng Real Madrid s sm hon tt thng v chuyn nhng De Gea trong t ngy ti. Theo iu lut ca UEFA, nu De Gea c tung ra sn trong trn u vi Club Brugge, anh vn c th thi u cho Real  u trng Champions League ma gii nm nay.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/12/41/degea1.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>De Gea khng c ng k thi u trn khai mc ma gii 2015/16</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Trn lt i vng play-off Champions League din ra vo ngy 18/8 ti trn sn Old Trafford v 1 tun sau trn lt v s din ra trn t B.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>i hnh Manchester United tham d trn u play-off gp Club Brugge:</div>\r\n<div>Th mn: David De Gea, Anders Lindegaard, Sergio Romero, Sam Johnstone.</div>\r\n<div>Hu v: Phil Jones, Marcos Rojo, Jonny Evans, Chris Smalling, Luke Shaw, Paddy McNair, Matteo Darmian, Tyler Blackett.</div