(3923, 2, '2015-08-15 23:12:44', '2015-08-15 16:12:44', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">Thng 4 nm 2001, Pepe Reina   lt li 8 bn thua ch trong 2 trn gp Villarreal v Zaragoza. K t  ti nay, Barca mi lp li thnh tch phng ng ti t y.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/31/terstegen15-8.jpg" alt="Ter Stegen lt li 8 bn ch sau 2 trn u ma" />Ter Stegen lt li 8 bn ch sau 2 trn u ma</div>\r\n<div>Ngay trong 2 trn u tin ca ma gii 2015/16, nh KV La Liga, Champions League v Cp Nh Vua   lt li 8 bn thua, 4 trc Sevilla  Siu cp chu u (thng 5-4) v 4 trc Athletic Bilbao  Siu cp TBN (<a class="news_ref" href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/19/128689/barcelona-thuc-thu-0-4-truoc-bilbao-trong-ngay-aduriz-lap-hat-trick.bdplus">thua 0-4 lt i</a>).</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Tm bn thua trong 2 trn u chnh thc vi mt i bng nh Barcelona l rt kh chp nhn, cho d ln gn nht h c thnh tch ti t nh th  cch y 14 nm, khi Villarreal v Zaragoza mi i ghi c 4 bn vo li ca Reina.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Villarreal 4-4 Barca</div>\r\n<div>Ngy 8/4/2001,  vng u th 29 ca La Liga, Barca hnh qun ti El Madrigal ca Villarreal v tri qua mt trn u nhc nhn v ci m, kt thc vi t s chung cuc 4-4.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Zaragoza 4-4 Barca</div>\r\n<div>Vng u tip theo, Barca c tr li Nou Camp ngy 14/4, nhng ht hip 1 bt ng  thua 2 bn trng. H chi tt hn trong hip 2, nhng cng  i phng ghi thm 2 bn na, khp li trn ha 4-4 th 2 lin tip. Rivaldo l tc gi bn thng cui cng  pht b gi.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/15/31/reina15-8.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>Reina l ngi trn gi khung thnh Barca vo nm 2001</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div> c 2 trn u trn, Reina u l ngi gc n ca Barca, pha trc l hng th gm Gabri, Michael Reiziger, Frank de Boer v Sergi. HLV trng ca i bng x Catalan khi y l Llorenc Serra Ferrer.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<h2>Ter Stegen   thng li bng na s bn thua c ma trc</h2>\r\n<div>Marc-Andre Ter Stegen   lt li 8 bn k t u ma, bng na s bn thua anh phi nhn sut c ma gii trc.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>D sao cng kh trch th thnh ngi c, bi ngoi tr bn thng m t s ca Mikel San Jose  trn thua Athletic Bilbao, 3 bn cn li u do li hng th hn l sai lm c nhn anh.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ma gii 2014/15, Ter Stegen  chi v cng n tng  Cp Nh Vua v Champions League vi 16 ln  thng li. ng tic l ngay  2 trn u ca ma 2015/16, anh  phi vo li nht bng ti mt na con s y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2 trn thua 8 bn, sau 14 nm Barca mi li t n th', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3906-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-15 23:12:44', '2015-08-15 16:12:44', '', 3906, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/3906-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
