(3949, 2, '2015-08-21 09:47:58', '2015-08-21 02:47:58', '<table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left" valign="middle"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left" valign="middle"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left" valign="middle"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center">\r\n<div class="art_header_text">Vi mc gi 20 triu euro, Nh KV Serie A  c s phc v ca hu v Alex Sandro (Porto).</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="style6" align="left" valign="top">\r\n<div class="art_content">\r\n<div align="justify">\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Sau thi gian di m phn hp ng, cui cng Juventus  tm c ting ni chung vi Porto trong thng v Alex Sandro. Theo , i bng B o Nha  ng   cu th ca mnh gia nhp Juventus vi mc gi 20 triu euro. Nh KV Serie A s phi tr thm 5 triu euro nu Sandro thi u thnh cng  ma gii ti.</span>\r\n<p align="center"><span style="font-family: arial;"><img src="http://static.goal.com/377700/377780_heroa.jpg" alt="" width="500" align="baseline" border="0" hspace="0" /></span></p>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Vo chiu ti qua (19/8), Alex Sandro  p chuyn bay sang Turin  lm th tc kim tra y t trc khi t bt k hp ng 5 nm vi Juventus. Ti y, hu v ngi Brazil s hng mc lng 3 triu euro/ma.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Thng v trn  c Gim c iu hnh Giuseppe Marotta v HLV Max Allegri xc nhn. V thuyn trng ca Juventus t ra rt hi lng vi bn hp ng mi ny.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Alex Sandro  ti! Cu ta s l s b sung hon ho cho i bng. Ti ngh chng ti c th hon tt thng v ny ngay trong ti nay, HLV Max Allegri chia s.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">S d Juventus phi chiu m Alex Sandro l bi Patrice Evra  bc sang tui 34, khng  th lc  cy i trn mi u trng. Trong khi , Kwadwo Asamoah vn cha hn ngy tr li. Trc khi theo ui hu v ngi Brazil, Nh KV Serie A tng m phn chiu m Guiherme Siqueira (Atletico) nhng li t ngt hy gia chng.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Alex Sandro, 24 tui, gia nhp Porto t Santos vo ma H nm 2011. y l bn hp ng th 6 ca Juventus trong phin ch H nm nay. Trc , Nh KV Serie A  c Paulo Dybala (Palermo), Mario Mandzukic (Atletico), Neto (Fiorentina), Sami Khedira (Real Madrid) v Simone Zaza (Sassuolo).</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Trong ngy hm nay, Sandro s lm th tc kim tra y t v k hp ng 5 nm vi Juventus. Theo xc nhn ca Gim c iu hnh Giuseppe Marotta, Juventus s chiu m thm 1 tin v tn cng na sau khi hon tt th tc mua Sandro. C 3 mc tiu chnh ang c Lo b quan tm l Isco (Real Madrid), Julian Draxler (Schalke) v Oscar (Chelsea).</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="art_center_banner"></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="middle"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Chi 20 triu euro, Juventus n tn binh th 6', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chi-20-trieu-euro-juventus-don-tan-binh-thu-6', '', '', '2015-08-21 09:47:58', '2015-08-21 02:47:58', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3949', 0, 'post', '', 0),
