e A tng m phn chiu m Guiherme Siqueira (Atletico) nhng li t ngt hy gia chng.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Alex Sandro, 24 tui, gia nhp Porto t Santos vo ma H nm 2011. y l bn hp ng th 6 ca Juventus trong phin ch H nm nay. Trc , Nh KV Serie A  c Paulo Dybala (Palermo), Mario Mandzukic (Atletico), Neto (Fiorentina), Sami Khedira (Real Madrid) v Simone Zaza (Sassuolo).</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Trong ngy hm nay, Sandro s lm th tc kim tra y t v k hp ng 5 nm vi Juventus. Theo xc nhn ca Gim c iu hnh Giuseppe Marotta, Juventus s chiu m thm 1 tin v tn cng na sau khi hon tt th tc mua Sandro. C 3 mc tiu chnh ang c Lo b quan tm l Isco (Real Madrid), Julian Draxler (Schalke) v Oscar (Chelsea).</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="art_center_banner"></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="middle"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Chi 20 triu euro, Juventus n tn binh th 6', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3949-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-21 09:47:58', '2015-08-21 02:47:58', '', 3949, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/3949-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3952, 2, '2015-08-21 09:49:41', '2015-08-21 02:49:41', '<table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="style6" align="left" valign="top"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class="art_brief">\r\n<h5>Inter quyt tm tr li  ma gii ny khi chiu m rt nhiu tn binh cht lng. Tuy nhin, vic i hnh qu xo trn c th gy kh cho on qun ca HLV Mancini.</h5>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="style6" align="left" valign="top">\r\n<div class="art_content">\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"><b>Sc mu mi ca Inter</b></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Sn bay Malpensa (Milan) trong ma H ny bng nhn nhp hn l thng. N nh thc hng triu tri tim Inter, vn  ngui lnh sau giai on trm ca i bng v ng thi nh thc c tham vng ca th lc hng u nc Italia.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="color: #0000cc; font-family: arial; font-size: small;"><i><img src="http://media.90min.com/process?url=http%3A%2F%2Fftbpro-post-images.s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com%2Fproduction%2F483802040&amp;filters%5Bcrop%5D%5Bw%5D=0.9982924482924483&amp;filters%5Bcrop%5D%5Bh%5D=0.8276785714285714&amp;filters%5Bcrop%5D%5Bo_x%5D=0.0&amp;filters%5Bcrop%5D%5Bo_y%5D=0.014285714285714285&amp;filters%5Bresize%5D%5Bw%5D=912&amp;filters%5Bresize%5D%5Bh%5D=516&amp;filters%5Bquality%5D%5Btarget%5D=80&amp;type=.jpg" alt="" width="500" align="none" /></i></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="color: #0000cc; font-family: arial; font-size: small;"><i>Nhng hp ng cht lng gip Inter vn tm</i></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Bu tri Milan dng nh xanh hn trong ting c v, h vang cho n hng lot ci tn Kondogbia (30 triu euro), Jeison Murillo (8 triu euro), Miranda (mn), Stevan Jovetic (mn), Martn Montoya (mn)</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">ng ch Thohir  khng ni di.  ma gii trc, ng  ha s ph tan bu khng kh u m v mang li thnh cng cho Inter bng nhng bn hp ng mi. Tnh ti thi im ny, Nerazzurri  vung ti 64 triu euro (c th nhiu hn na)  tng cng lc lng.  l con s ng ghi nhn trong bi cnh CLB va chu n pht t lut Cng bng ti chnh.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Ln u tin k t khi ln ngi  Champions League(2010), Inter mi tp np ti vy. Danh d ca i bng ln  hi thc h tr li. Gi y, i bng  mang sc mu mi y ti sng.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Nhiu chuyn gia nh gi, on qun ca HLV Mancini s tr thnh thch thc ng gm vi nh v ch Juventus  ma gii ny. R rng, h mnh ln trng thy so vi ma gii trc (t nht trn l thuyt) vi s b sung cht lng  3 tuyn.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"> hng th, s xut hin ca Miranda, Montoya, Jeison Murillo ha hn s gia c tuyn hu phng. Tuyn tin v cng c tng cng kh nng chin u cao vi Kondogbia (cha k hng lot cu th c bp khc nh Guarin, Assane Gnoukouri, Medel, Brozovi). Hng cng  b sung thm nhng ci tn cht lng l Joveti, Biabiany.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"><b>Cn nhiu hoi nghi</b></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Tt nhin, nhng phn tch  trn vn ch nm trn l thuyt. Thc t, s xo trn qu nhiu c th nh hng ln ti Inter. Gi y, HLV Mancini gn nh phi lm vic vi i hnh mi hon ton.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="color: #0000cc; font-family: arial; font-size: small;"><i><img src="http://www.irishtimes.com/polopoly_fs/1.2319601.1439799615!/image/image.jpg_gen/derivatives/box_620_330/image.jpg" alt="" width="500" align="none" /></i></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="color: #0000cc; font-family: arial; font-size: small;"><i>HLV Mancini cn rt nhiu vic phi lm</i></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Phong   lot trn giao hu va qua  cho thy iu . Trong 6 trn giao hu ngoi t Italia, Inter u mi ch thng 1 (trc Bilbao), ha 1, thua 4. Thm ch, h khng th ghi ni bn 5/6 trn u  (thua Bayern 0-1, thua Milan 0-1, thua Real 0-3, thua Galatasaray 0-1, ha AEK Athens 0-0).</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Vn bit rng nhng trn giao hu ma gii khng th ni ln iu g nhng n l li cnh bo  sc nng vi Inter trc thi im Serie A sp khi tranh, nht l khi li chi ca CLB vn kh th cng.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Gi y, HLV Mancini cn phi bin nim vui trn giy t thnh n ci trn sn c.  vn ti chc v ch l iu kh khn (bi Juve qu mnh) nhng ch cn ginh v d Champions League cng l thnh cng ln vi Inter.</span></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Serie A 2015/16: Inter - Tham vng c tha nhng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'serie-a-201516-inter-tham-vong-co-thua-nhung', '', '', '2015-08-21 09:49:41', '2015-08-21 02:49:41', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3952', 0, 'post', '', 0),
