(3957, 2, '2015-08-21 09:51:00', '2015-08-21 02:51:00', '<table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="style6" align="left" valign="top"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class="art_brief">\r\n<h5>CLB Porto chnh thc xc nhn bn hu v tri ngi Brazil Alex Sandro cho pha Juventus.</h5>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="style6" align="left" valign="top">\r\n<div class="art_content">\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Cch y t gi, CLB Porto chnh thc xc nhn  nhng li hu v tri ngi Brazil Alex Sandro cho Juventus. Trong khi , v pha Juventus, trn trang ch i bng ny cho bit  k hp ng 5 nm vi</span>Sandro.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">c bit,  c c ch k ca</span>Sandro, Juventus  phi chi tr cho i bng B o Nha mt khon tin tr gi 26 triu euro.Sandro chnh l bn hp ng th 7 ca Juventus trong ma H ny, sau<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Mario Mandzukic, Sami Khedira, Paulo Dybala, Simone Zaza, Neto v Guido Vadala.</span></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://bongdaso.com/images/Article/Upload/150821_001904_709.jpg" alt="" width="500" align="none" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Alex Sandro c Juve a v nhm cnh tranh vi Patrice Evra  v tr hu v tri. Ngoi ra, Juve cng xem Sandro l cu th thay th Evra trong tng lai.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Trc khi chiu m Sandro, Juventus c cho l nhm ti Guilherme Siqueira ca Atletico Madrid. Tuy vy, h  thay i nhanh chng khi bit c Sandro khng c  nh gia hn hp ng vi Porto.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Trn thc t, y l mt s thay i sng sut ca B m gi bi l Siqueira  29 tui, trong khi  Sandro mi 24 v hon ton c th thi u sung sc thm t nht 5 hoc 6 nm na.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;"></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: small;">Sandro chuyn ti thi u cho Porto vo nm 2011 t Santos. Khng mt qu nhiu thi gian, Sandro  khng nh c tn tui trong mu o i bng mi. K t sau khi cp bn CLB ca B o Nha. Sandro thi u 86 trn v ghi 5 bn.</span></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;', 'CHNH THC: Juventus n thm sao b', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3955-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-21 09:51:00', '2015-08-21 02:51:00', '', 3955, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/3955-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3958, 2, '2015-08-21 09:54:49', '2015-08-21 02:54:49', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">D b dn trc 3 bn trn sn khch nhng Borussia Dortmund  c mn ngc dng in r  chim u th trc trn lt v, trong khi Athletic Bilbao li khng c may mn nh th ti lt i play-off Europa League.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox">\r\n<div class="mediaitem"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/21/31/dortmundcrazy21-8.jpg" alt="Dortmund c mn li ngc dng in r ti Na Uy" /></div>\r\nDortmund c mn li ngc dng in r ti Na Uy\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Sm b thng li sau 2 pht vi qu nh u ca Jone Samuelsen, Dortmund cng chi cng lung cung v cha y 30 pht, t s  l 3-0 nghing v pha i ch nh Odd Ballklub (Na Uy). Nhng ri c p ca Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang cng cc pha lp cng ca Shinji Kagawa v Henrikh Mkhitaryan  gip thy tr Thomas Tuchel hon tt mn ngc dng ngon mc  ginh li th trc trn lt v.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Tri ngc vi Dortmund, Athletic Bilbao  khi u khng th tt hn trn t Slovakia. Cc bn thng ca Sabin Merino v Kike Sola gip i din Ty Ban Nha vt ln dn trc 2-0 ngay t hip 1, nhng 3 bn thua trong vng 25 pht cui  khin Bilbao thc th chung cuc trc ch nh Zilina. Jakub Paur l tc gi bn g u tin, trc khi William lp c p gip  qun Slovakia thng ngc 3-2.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/21/31/vanpersiegoal21-8.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>Van Persie em v thng li qu gi cho Fenerbahce</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Trn t Hy Lp, Fenerbahce  tri qua mt trn u nhc nhn trc ch nh Atromitos. Rt may l  pht cui cng, h c c bn thng duy nht nh cng ca tin o tn binh Robin van Persie, ngi ch c tung vo sn t pht 80.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ti St Marys, i din nc Anh Southampton  phi cn ti pha lp cng u tin sau 17 thng tri ca tin o Jay Rodriguez  vt vt li mt kt qu ha 1-1 trc i khch Midtjylland. ng ni l chnh cu cu th Soton, Tim Sparv l tc gi bn m t s cho i din an Mch.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>c thi u trn sn nh nhng Ajax  gy tht vng khi ch nh bi i din CH Czech vi chin thng ti thiu. Arkadiusz Milik l tc gi pha lm bn duy nht cho i ch sn Amsterdam Arena t chm 11m sau tnh hung phm li ca Vit Benes vi Davy Klaassen.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Lt i play-off Europa League: Dortmund thng ngc ''in r'' sau khi b dn 3 bn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'luot-di-play-off-europa-league-dortmund-thang-nguoc-dien-ro-sau-khi-bi-dan-3-ban', '', '', '2015-08-21 09:54:49', '2015-08-21 02:54:49', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3958', 0, 'post', '', 0),
