(3961, 2, '2015-08-21 09:56:50', '2015-08-21 02:56:50', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">Angel Di Maria ra mt PSG v i bng ca anh thng d GFC Ajaccio, nhng y l trn u ca Marco Verratti.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/18/26/danan.jpg" alt="Verratti (phi) chi rt ni bt trong chin thng 2-0 trc GFC Ajaccio" />Verratti (phi) chi rt ni bt trong chin thng 2-0 trc GFC Ajaccio\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Trong cuc n tip GFC Ajaccio rng sng qua, Verratti khng thc hin c ng kin to no, cng khng ghi bn thng no, nhng anh li l trm trung chuyn bng quan trng nht ca i nh. C th ni anh l nim cm hng quan trng nht mang li 3 im cho PSG khi mi ng bng thu hi hay pht ng tn cng cng u qua chn ca tin v nh con ny.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Theo thng k ca BTC Ligue 1, Verratti va ph k lc chuyn bng nhiu nht trong mt trn u  tn ti sut 10 nm qua ti gii VQG Php vi 142 ng chuyn (trong  130 ng ti ng a ch, t l chnh xc 90%).</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ngoi ra Verratti cn c 156 ln chm bng, tim cn k lc 158 ng chuyn mt trn ti Ligue 1 m chnh anh lp ra  ma trc. V nu nh ma gii nm ngoi, gii chuyn mn cn ch kh nng chuyn di ca Verratti th gi h s phi xem xt li. Bi trong s 142 ng chuyn ca anh  trn gp GFC Ajaccio, ch c 25 ng chuyn di c ly 30m.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/18/26/verratti.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>Marco Verratti ang chng t l nhn t quan trng bc nht  PSG</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>iu  cho thy k nng chi bng thng tha cng nh kh nng iu phi bng tuyt vi ca Verratti. Cu th tr ngi Italia vn ang pht trin mnh m ln tm cao mi.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Trong cc hip 2 trn u vi Lille  vng  mn v trn u hm qua, 60% ng chuyn ca Verratti c a ch nhn l Thiago Motta. Hai tin v ngi Italia ny phi hp cc k nhun nhuyn. C l,  l mt trong nhng l do ti sao PSG ang phi thuyt phc bng c Motta gia hn hp ng. V mt khi tri thnh cng Motta, chc hn BL i bng thnh Paris s thm cm n Verratti.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'PSG thng d GFC Ajaccio: Du n Verratti', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'psg-thang-de-gfc-ajaccio-dau-an-verratti', '', '', '2015-08-21 09:56:50', '2015-08-21 02:56:50', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3961', 0, 'post', '', 0),
