(3964, 2, '2015-08-21 09:58:44', '2015-08-21 02:58:44', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">Dnh chn thng u gi phi  chin thng 2-0 trc Lyon ti trn tranh Siu Cp Php ngy 1/8 va qua, tin o Zlatan Ibrahimovic vn cha hi phc  luyn tp cng ng i. Cha bao gi nhng ngi yu mn PSG mong s tr li ca tin o k cu ngi Thy in nh lc ny.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/20/25/ibra.jpg" alt="Ibra vn phi tp ring di s gim st ca cc bc s" />Ibra vn phi tp ring di s gim st ca cc bc s\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Bi trn thc t, y l thi im m KV Ligue 1 nh Ibra hn bao gi ht khi hng cng vn hnh km hiu qu, m c th l Edinson Cavani.  2 vng u u tin ca Ligue 1 2015/16, tin o ngi Uruguay u thi u di phong , c<a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/28/128959/psg-thang-de-gfc-ajaccio-dau-an-verratti.bdplus">c chn st khc cng khng t yu cu v km hiu qu.</a></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>im sng duy nht l Lucas Moura. Song, cu th ngi Brazil c thi quen ch bng n vi trn u  ma gii mi, ri chm nghm sau  t khi n Parc des Princes. Chnh v th, PSG rt cuc vn cn n ng cp ca lo tng 34 tui ngi Thy in. Theo thng tin t bc s PSG, Ibra gn nh chc chn vng mt trong chuyn lm khch ti Montpellier (vng 3) cui tun ny.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ibra hin vn phi theo ch  vn ng ring c s gim st ca cc nhn vin y t. Cu y cha ly li c 100% th lc. Tuy nhin, ti hi lng v s tin trin trong chn thng ca Ibra v khin ti yn tm hn. Nhiu kh nng Ibra s tr li vo tun ti, HLV Laurent Blanc t ra rt thn trng khi ni v s tr li ca tin o ngi Thy in.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/20/25/ibra1.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>Ibrahimovic vn ang trong giai on dng thng</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>S d, PSG thn trng vi chn thng ca Ibra n th, v  trnh vo vt xe  ca ma trc. Vi chn thng lng cha bnh phc hon ton, Ibra vn c gng thi u ri li ti pht v dnh thm vi chn thng khc an xem. Hu qu, anh ch chi c vn vn 24 trn v ghi c 19 bn ti gii VQG Php ma trc.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>D chun b sinh nht tui 34 (3/10), nhng Ibra vn l tin o khng th thay th trn hng cng PSG. V Blanc s khng th mo him tung anh vo sn khi Ibra cha sn sng, nht l vn  th lc.</div>\r\n<div>D kin Ibra ra sn sm nht l chuyn lm khch rt quan trng ti Monaco (31/8), d cha chc  c c trn.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ma trc, Ibra dnh 4 chn thng cc loi an xen nhau v b treo gi 5 trn khin tng s ln ra sn ca anh ch khim tn l 35 trn trn mi u trng, km xa so vi 2 ma u tin khoc o KV Php, ln lt l 46 v 45 trn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grd11"></div>', 'PSG: Cui thng ny Ibra mi c th tr li', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'psg-cuoi-thang-nay-ibra-moi-co-the-tro-lai', '', '', '2015-08-21 09:58:44', '2015-08-21 02:58:44', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3964', 0, 'post', '', 0),
