(3966, 2, '2015-08-21 09:58:44', '2015-08-21 02:58:44', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">Dnh chn thng u gi phi  chin thng 2-0 trc Lyon ti trn tranh Siu Cp Php ngy 1/8 va qua, tin o Zlatan Ibrahimovic vn cha hi phc  luyn tp cng ng i. Cha bao gi nhng ngi yu mn PSG mong s tr li ca tin o k cu ngi Thy in nh lc ny.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/20/25/ibra.jpg" alt="Ibra vn phi tp ring di s gim st ca cc bc s" />Ibra vn phi tp ring di s gim st ca cc bc s\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Bi trn thc t, y l thi im m KV Ligue 1 nh Ibra hn bao gi ht khi hng cng vn hnh km hiu qu, m c th l Edinson Cavani.  2 vng u u tin ca Ligue 1 2015/16, tin o ngi Uruguay u thi u di phong , c<a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/28/128959/psg-thang-de-gfc-ajaccio-dau-an-verratti.bdplus">c chn st khc cng khng t yu cu v km hiu qu.</a></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>im sng duy nht l Lucas Moura. Song, cu th ngi Brazil c thi quen ch bng n vi trn u  ma gii mi, ri chm nghm sau  t khi n Parc des Princes. Chnh v th, PSG rt cuc vn cn n ng cp ca lo tng 34 tui ngi Thy in. Theo thng tin t bc s PSG, Ibra gn nh chc chn vng mt trong chuyn lm khch ti Montpellier (vng 3) cui tun ny.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ibra hin vn phi theo ch  vn ng ring c s gim st ca cc nhn vin y t. Cu y cha ly li c 100% th lc. Tuy nhin, ti hi lng v s tin trin trong chn thng ca Ibra v khin ti yn tm hn. Nhiu kh nng Ibra s tr li vo tun ti, HLV Laurent Blanc t ra rt thn trng khi ni v s tr li ca tin o ngi Thy in.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/20/25/ibra1.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div>Ibrahimovic vn ang trong giai on dng thng</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>S d, PSG thn trng vi chn thng ca Ibra n th, v  trnh vo vt xe  ca ma trc. Vi chn thng lng cha bnh phc hon ton, Ibra vn c gng thi u ri li ti pht v dnh thm vi chn thng khc an xem. Hu qu, anh ch chi c vn vn 24 trn v ghi c 19 bn ti gii VQG Php ma trc.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>D chun b sinh nht tui 34 (3/10), nhng Ibra vn l tin o khng th thay th trn hng cng PSG. V Blanc s khng th mo him tung anh vo sn khi Ibra cha sn sng, nht l vn  th lc.</div>\r\n<div>D kin Ibra ra sn sm nht l chuyn lm khch rt quan trng ti Monaco (31/8), d cha chc  c c trn.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ma trc, Ibra dnh 4 chn thng cc loi an xen nhau v b treo gi 5 trn khin tng s ln ra sn ca anh ch khim tn l 35 trn trn mi u trng, km xa so vi 2 ma u tin khoc o KV Php, ln lt l 46 v 45 trn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="grd11"></div>', 'PSG: Cui thng ny Ibra mi c th tr li', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3964-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-21 09:58:44', '2015-08-21 02:58:44', '', 3964, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/3964-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3967, 2, '2015-08-21 10:00:03', '2015-08-21 03:00:03', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">Sau khi b rt nhiu HLV t chi, Marseille  tm c ngi cn tm l Michel, cu HLV Olympiakos v Sevilla. Chin lc gia ngi Ty Ban Nha va c mi ngi vo gh nng  sn Velodrome vo ti qua, th ch Marcelo Bielsa.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/20/25/marseille.jpg" alt="Ch tch Labrune v HLV Michel (tri) trong l mt Marseille" />Ch tch Labrune v HLV Michel (tri) trong l mt Marseille\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>SM CHM DT CNH RN MT U</div>\r\n<div>10 ngy sau khi Marcelo Bielsa bt ng t chc, Marseille vn trong cnh ri nh canh h. Bi d c phn ng nhanh th no trong vic tm ngi thay th G in, Marseille cng khng thu c kt qu kh quan khi hu ht nhng HLV danh ting v c h s tt u  t chi ngi vo chic gh nng ti sn Velodrome.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Sau tht bi 0-1 trc Reims  vng 2 Ligue 1 va qua di s ch o ca HLV tm quyn Frank Passi, BL Marseille mi ng ra rng cn phi sm n nh tnh hnh vi mt nh cm qun thc s, i nh may ra mi ra c khi khng hong. V Michel  c chn.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Cui tun ny, Marseille s n tip Troyes  vng 3 Ligue 1. Ch tch Vincent Labrune nhn mnh rng, ng mun sm tm c HLV mi cho Marseille  hon tt nhng b sung lc lng. Bi u thng 9 ti, Ligue 1 s tm ngh  cc TQG tp trung thi u cho vng loi EURO 2016 v giao hu quc t. y s l khong thi gian qu bu cho Marseille chun b li mi th vi 1 HLV mi.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Chnh v th, Marseille hi lng v Michel, m trn thc t c ci tn rt di v kh nh: Jose Gonzalez Martin Del Campo! Chin lc gia 52 tui ny tng l cu cu th Real (1982-1996) v ang t do sau khi b Olympiakos sa thi ngy 6/1/2015. Trc khi b mt vic, Michel gip Olympiakos ginh ngi  qun gii VQG Hy Lp sau 16 vng v th 3  vng bng Champions League 2014/15 (sau Atletico v Juventus).</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Trc , Michel tng ginh 2 chc VQG Hy Lp 2013 v 2014; 1 Cp QG Hy Lp 2013. Qu trnh m phn gia Marseille v Michel din ra cc sun s v nhanh chng. Michel thm ch  ch ng xem ht i hnh cng nh video cc trn u ca Marseille t giai on chy  ma ny.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/20/25/marseille1.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>MARSEILLE CH I G  MICHEL?</div>\r\n<div>Tuy nhin, nhn vo h s kh n gin v s si ca Michel th r rng nhng ngi yu mn Marseille cha th yn tm. Michel mi ch thnh cng  gii VQG Hy Lp. Marseille trng i g vo Michel, hay h qu thc bch trong vic phi tm ra mt HLV trng? Thc ra, ch tch Labrune cho bit, ng ang hc cch tuyn ngi ca Monaco v Lyon.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>C hai i bng ny u chn nhng HLV v danh dn dt CLB  H 2014 v cng thu li kt qu rt ng khch l. Nu Leonardo Jardim (v danh trc khi n sn Louis II) gip Monaco vt qua mt ma H chy mu ti nng v v ch th 3 Ligue 1 2014/15, th Hubert Fournier (mi ch c 1 nm dn dt Reims ti Ligue 1) a i bng tr Lyon ginh ngi  qun ma trc y thuyt phc.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Chng ti cn s nhit tnh, tm huyt ca mt ngi nh Michel. ng y c th gip vc dy tinh thn cc cu th Marseille, hin vn cn sc v hoang mang sau s ra i bt ng ca Bielsa, Labrune tit l mt trong nhng nguyn nhn khin Marseille rt nhit tnh m phn vi Michel. Nh th, la chn chin lc gia ngi Ty Ban Nha c th ch l gii php tnh th ca i ch sn Veledrome.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>Hp ng vi Michel c thi hn bao lu?</div>\r\n<div>Marseille  chnh thc thng bo tin b nhim HLV Michel nhng li t chi tit l iu khon v thi hn cng nh mc lng ca bn hp ng vi chin lc gia ngi TBN ny. Ngun tin ca t bo a phng La Provence th cho hay, hp ng nng hi ny c thi hn 2 nm.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>VI NT V MICHEL</div>\r\n<div>Tn y : Jose Gonzalez Martin Del Campo</div>\r\n<div>Sinh ngy: 23/3/1963 (52 tui) ti Madrid, Ty Ban Nha</div>\r\n<div>Cc CLB tng dn dt: Vallecano, Real Madrid B, Getafe, Sevilla, Olympiakos v Marseille</div>\r\n<div>Thnh tch: 2 chc VQG Hy Lp (2012/13, 2013/14), 1 Cp QG Hy Lp (2012/13).</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Marseille b nhim Michel lm HLV trng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'marseille-bo-nhiem-michel-lam-hlv-truong', '', '', '2015-08-21 10:00:03', '2015-08-21 03:00:03', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3967', 0, 'post', '', 0),
