(3970, 2, '2015-08-21 10:02:02', '2015-08-21 03:02:02', '<div class="grd11">\r\n<p class="summary">Mt s lnh o ca cc CLB tn tui gp mt ti V-League tng tuyn b xanh rn: Nu khng ot c chc v ch th thi, ch cc huy chng khc th u v ngha!. Nhng thc t c phi vy khng?</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cl10"></div>\r\n<div id="grdContNews">\r\n<div class="grd8">\r\n<div class="contentbox">\r\n<div class="thumbnailsbox"><img class="thumb30" src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/21/25/hcd.jpg" alt="C Hi Phng (tri) v HN.T&amp;T u ang rt quyt tm ginh v tr th 3 chung cuc" />C Hi Phng (tri) v HN.T&amp;T u ang rt quyt tm ginh v tr th 3 chung cuc.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Ngoi B.Bnh Dng lun kht khao v ch, H Ni T&amp;T cng lun l mt ng vin sng gi  cuc ua ngi u. Th nhng, khi ma gii ang  giai on v ch v i bng H thnh vn ang  kh xa so vi i th chnh B.BD (km 8 im), lnh o i bng Th   c nhng toan tnh cho mc tiu thc t hn.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Trc mt H Ni T&amp;T l chuyn lm khch ti Hi Phng. Hin i ch nh ng  v tr th 3 vi 36 im, trong lc H Ni T&amp;T c 34 im v ang xp v tr th 5. Nh vy, khong cch ch l 2 im. Chnh v th m thy tr HLV Phan Thanh Hng ang rt mun ginh c 3 im  cuc i u ny  c th lt vo nhm c huy chng, trc khi toan tnh xa hn.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Xt nhiu gc , Hi Phng d ang hn v im s v c chi trn sn nh, nhng phong  ca h kh php ph trong thi gian qua. Ngc li, H Ni T&amp;T ang cho thy s hi sinh kh n tng  giai on 2 vi 12 trn lin tip bt bi. Nhng iu  cho thy, cuc u ca hai i vo cui tun ny ha hn s rt hp dn.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><img src="http://static.bongdaplus.vn/Assets/Media/2015/08/21/25/hcd1.jpg" alt="" border="0px" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Nu i bng ln nh<a href="http://bongdaplus.vn/tin-bai/3/128976/hn-t-t-chuyen-huong-muc-tieu.bdplus"> H Ni T&amp;T cn phi chuyn hng ch ngm</a> th mt CLB c u t rt nhiu  u ma vi nhiu tham vng nh Than Qung Ninh chc chn s khng mun ri cuc chi vi hai bn tay trng. Thi im ny, nu ni Than Qung Ninh vn mng m ua tranh ngi v ch th e l khng hp l, nhng h vn hon ton c th lt vo nhm c huy chng bi vi v tr th 6 trn bng tng sp cng 33 im, i bng t M hon ton c th t c mc tiu y.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Ngoi ra, nhng ci tn nh Sanna Khnh Ha, SLNA, T.LA v c SHB  Nng cng ang m v chic HC. Thm ch, mt HLV tng ni na a na tht: Nu khng v ch c th c m lt vo nhm c huy chng  khngung cng tranh u c ma gii. Mo m c hn khng m.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Cng cn nhc l  ma gii ti s c AFF Champions League, nn nu lt vo Top 3 V-League 2015, bit u s c c hi  gp mt tranh ti  sn chi quc t ny?!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>V th, chic HC tng b xem l vt i trong suy ngh ca nhiu ng ln, gi bng tr nn rt c gi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'V.League 2015: Ai m chic HC?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'v-league-2015-ai-mo-chiec-hcd', '', '', '2015-08-21 10:02:02', '2015-08-21 03:02:02', '', 0, 'http://bongda-az.com/az/?p=3970', 0, 'post', '', 0),
